title: Ent Mobile Banking
description:
Convenient, fast, secure and free – Ent’s Mobile Banking App allows you to easily review your account balances and history, transfer funds, make loan payments, pay bills, deposit checks, track your budget and more! 


Features:
•  View available account balances and last five transactions with just a tap 
•  Transfer funds between Ent accounts and to other financial institutions 
•  Make loan payments and pay bills
•  Deposit checks
•  View detailed account information including balances, history, statements and check images
•  Get an at-a-glance summary of your spending and saving activity
•  Manage alerts and notifications
•  View the most recent loan rates and apply for a loan
•  Customize your account by opening new checking, savings or certificate accounts on-the-go
•  Find ATMs and Service Centers
•  Reset or update your Username or Password

Your personal financial information security is our top priority. Ent uses advanced encryption technology to safeguard your information, and no account information is stored on your device. For more information on how Ent protects your personal financial information, visit Ent.com.

Ent Mobile Banking App users must be registered users of Ent’s Online Banking. There is no charge from Ent for any Ent Mobile Banking App service; however standard/other charges from your mobile service provider may apply.
